CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 27, 1962, pg. 1, reads: "HDCC Planners - The committee of the Hill District Community Council planning its annual award dinner, includes (left to right: Mary N. Smith, Martha Tyson, Alma A. Polk, Marian Downer, Ann John (standing) Walter Worthington, Gloria Grate, Nellye Barron, Pronty Ford, Dorothy Moore, Robert Lavelle, Rose Wallace and Roberta Hill. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Hill District Community Council members, seated from left: Mary N. Smith, Martha Tyson, Alma A. Polk, Marian Downer, Ann John; standing: Walter Worthington, Gloria Golden Grate, Nellye Barron, Pronty Ford, Dorothy Moore, Robert Lavelle, Rose Wallace and Roberta Hill posed in interior with painting
